snippet.title: Gameplay Noroi E: The Origin PROTOTYPE
snippet.description:
Download it at the following link:

BETA v0.4
https://ciberflystudios.itch.io/

Wishlist Now On Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2411320/Noroi_E_The_Origin_of_Nightmares/?beta=0

You can Tag the Game On Twitch Categories...

Thanks to everyone who supports our projects, it´s very inspiring, thank you for giving us the oportunity to develop and do what we love.

Don´t forget that you can support us in our patreon account to have the opportunity to contribute to the development of this project.

https://www.patreon.com/CiberFlyStudios

You can also follow us on our social networks to not miss exclusive previews for the next versions of the game.

Discord: https://discord.gg/VbkFSC558X

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CiberFlyStudios
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/NoroiETheOrigin
Twitter: https://twitter.com/ciberflystudios
Tik Tok: https://www.tiktok.com/@ciberflystudios

Soon you will be able to add our game  to your Steam Wish List.

Mixer: Cristian D. García M.
